author: Source: Ludlow Advertiser
title: Pakistan captain Misbah-ul-Haq believes England have learned from past mistakes - Ludlow Advertiser
text:
Misbah-ul-Haq expects England to have learned from the mistakes they made in their whitewash defeat on their only previous Test tour of the United Arab Emirates. Captain Alastair Cook is one of four players returning, after figuring under his predecessor Andrew Strauss in the 3-0 defeat against Pakistan almost four years ago.
 Ludlow Advertiser.
